<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo.png" type="image/x-icon">
  <title>Delete My Data - OmniWatch</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
      color: #e2e8f0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
    header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
      padding-bottom: 30px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #334155;
    }
    h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .updated { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 1rem; }
    h2 {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin: 35px 0 15px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #3b82f6;
    }
    .section {
      background: #1e293b;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #334155;
    }
    .section h3 {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    p { color: #cbd5e1; }
    ul { color: #cbd5e1; margin-left: 20px; }
    li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .steps {
      background: #0f172a;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      border-left: 3px solid #3b82f6;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 50px;
      padding-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #334155;
      color: #64748b;
    }
    footer a { color: #3b82f6; text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>Delete My Data</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: February 27, 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class="section">
      <h3>1. Delete Your Account</h3>
      <p>To delete all your data, simply delete your account from the Settings page in the mobile app.
      When you delete your account, all associated data is automatically and permanently removed at the same time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h3>2. No Separate Request Needed</h3>
      <p>You do not need to send a separate data deletion request. Deleting your account removes all
      your data from our servers immediately. We do not retain any user data after account deletion.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h3>3. What Data is Deleted</h3>
      <p>When you delete your account, the following data is permanently removed:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Account details (name, phone number, role, organization)</li>
        <li>All patrol assignments</li>
        <li>All patrol activity records</li>
        <li>All log entries and notes</li>
        <li>Any uploaded images</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h3>4. Data Retention</h3>
      <p>We do not keep any copies of your data after deletion. Once your account is deleted, all your
      information is completely removed from our systems and cannot be recovered.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h3>5. How to Delete Your Account</h3>
      <p>To delete your account and all associated data:</p>
      <div class="steps">1. Open the Settings tab in the OmniWatch mobile app</div>
      <div class="steps">2. Scroll down to the "Danger Zone" section</div>
      <div class="steps">3. Tap on "Delete Account"</div>
      <div class="steps">4. Confirm your decision when prompted</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h3>6. Contact</h3>
      <p>If you have any questions about data deletion, contact your administrator or OmniWatch support.</p>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <p><a href="/privacy-policy">← Back to Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="/">← Back to Home</a></p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>